          <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p1"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">景区简介</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/90931477384731.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p>从石家庄出发到青虚山，全程约160公里，自驾约2.5小时。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/f944915f13e9610fb1c46fb286626024.jpg" alt="" title=""/><strong>第一天：青虚山</strong></p><p>青虚山景区位于最高峰海拔998米，三主峰座和十几座峰林构成了景区特有的地貌景观，风景区内秀峰林立，峡谷幽深，还有参天古树，飞瀑甘泉。</p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/5061477384731.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p><strong>第二天：大石峪（潭瀑峡）</strong></p><p>大石峪景区现为国家AAA级景区，国家级森林公园。景区西南部是自然保护区，有上世纪70年代飞播松林。</p><p><br/></p>            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p2"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">交通路线</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/bb506861977bb1775663ebf3b3cc8385.png" alt="" title=""/>​</p><p><strong>自驾：</strong></p><p>从石家庄到青虚山，沿路线：京昆高速——保阜高速——军白线——青虚山，全程160公里，用时约2.5小时。</p><p>从青虚山到大石峪（潭瀑峡），沿路线：S332——大石峪（潭瀑峡），全程约50公里，用时约1.5小时。</p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/16191477384861.png" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p><strong>乘车：</strong></p><p>从石家庄坐火车到保定后转乘到唐县的班车，从唐县客运站坐到村里的汽车即可，倒车麻烦且不好找，建议自驾。</p><p><br/></p>            </div>
          </div>
                    <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p4"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">时间安排</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/d9c7dc318da87350040808a3ca445023.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​<strong>第一天：</strong></p><p>早上出发，近中午到达青虚山，下午游览完毕后，晚上驱车前往大石峪（潭瀑峡）附近农家院入住。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><strong>第二天 ：</strong></p><p>早餐后，游览大石峪（潭瀑峡），下午返回石家庄。</p><p><br/></p> </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p5"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">DAY1：青虚山</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div> </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p5-0"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">玩什么</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/39931477384995.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p>青虚山景区位于河北省唐县齐家佐乡境内，最高峰海拔998米，三主峰座和十几座峰林构成了景区特有的地貌景观。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/0f6b9ab910be6465d9a166360c40b925.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/c03ce223c62c9fad28bf0687dc6e1bec.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>风景区内秀峰林立，峡谷幽深，还有参天古树，飞瀑甘泉。<br/></p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/53e9f8a0f728b1e38a6ff88966b8203e.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/94d8f28a022ab06b3bf43754d2426c93.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/04c7a577568089ac638f396a2cd88d59.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>青虚山多为石灰岩，久经风雨溶蚀，形成了“如青笋、似狼牙、像箭镞、直刺云天”的奇峰峻岭。<br/></p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/93a54cfc39fec90679fea8ef5106fddb.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p><br/></p><p>一年四季溪水常流，秀丽的两处龙潭，显得灵气十足。</p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/70041477384995.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/24011477384995.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p>青虚山有紫云峰等四峰、三岩、九洞、四峪、二园、二寨、二崖、二潮等自然景观40余处。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/3f276e575abe2e201745b356748db6bc.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/4a58d7d0b12bcfd42bbc99d3763b89b8.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p><p>远眺此山，“万峰耸翠，霁瞑不时，烟霞无定，青虚耸翠”，为唐县古八景之一。<br/></p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/3051477384995.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p>            </div>
          </div>
                    <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p5-1"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">住哪里</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p>傍晚在青虚山游览完毕后驱车到大石峪（潭瀑峡）附近农家院入住，价位在100元左右。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/6e6a166b1a0552ce010fa0c553346968.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p>            </div>
          </div>
                    <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p5-2"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">吃什么</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p>可在农家院尝一些农家绿色食品，价格都不太贵。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/33fbda530acf6913bba9183befdb5187.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p>            </div>
          </div>
                    <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p5-3"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">买什么</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p>唐县大枣以“个大、核小、皮薄、肉厚”著称，为枣中之上乘佳品，久负盛名。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/ef4a972110002b47be6b7ed5daf00947.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p>            </div>
          </div>
                                        <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p6"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">DAY2：大石峪（潭瀑峡）</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div> </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p6-0"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">玩什么</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/26681477385136.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p>在潭瀑峪景区中部段家庄村口，有一棵树龄1500多年的枫树，2000年被唐县人民政府命名为“枫树王”。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/93ae087d72aae9b2ec9b936add4ef947.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/39737d6a2ed6eceacdae41513b25b2b0.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>景区内山峦叠嶂，峡谷幽深，地质结构多为花岗岩和片麻岩。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/d1b1b1dfd06f1e2cdb10a6f9e7a5d998.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/22a2515d604cc74b60fcd03adef12fdb.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/58160751298a18b3926472f5761aa2f2.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>地表水土保持较好，因而形成了多潭多瀑景观。景区内水质清澈甘甜，经化验符合国家一级水标准。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/cb3b780f6f07e0c88becd29a2848e2d6.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/1976f49aac41b79e6f4b91dee097177f.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/a8f5cf4576924c9d52546739d3640008.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>景区内巨石累累，卵石滚滚故得此名——大石峪。<br/></p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/f7a01a1aac41af9faf083e622c37d5ea.jpg" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/639e9cac39cf23622dafa292047276f4.jpg" alt="" title=""/></p><p>大石峪给人的印象就是水多石头多。到处都是哗哗碧水，满眼都是滚滚银石。<br/></p><p><img src="http://www.aitto.net/uploads/arcimgs/25731477385136.jpg" alt="" title="" style="white-space: normal;"/></p><p>到此一游，你会真正体验到清泉石上流，人在水中游的乐趣。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/79a8ddadba9dbbb772361bca6f56b54b.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p>            </div>
          </div>
                    <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-child"> <a class="ebma-anchor1" href="#" id="p6-1"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-child"><span class="head-con">吃什么</span></h4>
            <div class="ebma-con">
              <p>午餐在西胜沟农家院吃或者自带食物。</p><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/c8ffc6c6c9f49b96f38aa10c7d0dee56.jpg" alt="" title=""/>​</p>            </div>
          </div>
                                        <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p7"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">小贴士</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p>1、夏秋季节最适合参观游览。</p><p>2、青虚山不收门票，潭瀑峡（大石峪）门票30元，漂流50元。</p><p>3、漂流的话需提前备好干爽衣物，保护好相机。</p><p>4、道教名山圣地，香火旺盛，特别是每年农历三月十五各地香客前来进香，非常壮观。</p><p><br/></p> </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p8"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">看别人怎么说</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/b595169de620766a5cbb52044f045400.png" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/2793ed45bc28d94d1d8ff22f582248da.png" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/c621baf3ac4d85d7db651020cdd7829a.png" alt="" title=""/><img src="/new_uploads/2016/1025/c3f66644dc00439ac17c905febcccb9b.png" alt="" title=""/></p> </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p9"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">小编说</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p>青虚山满坡满坡的葛藤和灌木，泉水飞溅，一派南国风光。大石峪给人的印象就是水多石头多。到处都是哗哗碧水，满眼都是滚滚银石。到此一游，你会真正体验到清泉石上流，人在水中游的乐趣。</p> </div>
